																		</div>
																	</div>
																	<div class="item-subtitle">Fuel Logistics</div>
																	<div class="item-description">Specialized
																		transportation of petroleum products carried out
																		under strict safety and compliance standards,
																		guaranteeing secure handling and dependable fuel
																		delivery.</div>
																</div>
																<div id="item-c07005b" class="box-content ">
																	<div class="item-image">
																		<div class="col-auto">
																			<img loading="lazy" decoding="async"
