																		</div>
																	</div>
																	<div class="item-subtitle">Tank Hire</div>
																	<div class="item-description">Flexible fuel tank
																		hiring solutions for short- or long-term use,
																		supported by proper logistics planning and safe,
																		compliant storage systems.</div>
																</div>
																<div id="item-9b39387" class="box-content ">
																	<div class="item-image">
																		<div class="col-auto">
																			<img loading="lazy" decoding="async"
