														<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-7e8725d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child"
															data-id="7e8725d" data-element_type="container">
															<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-74bf464 elementor-widget elementor-widget-pxl_services_list"
																data-id="74bf464" data-element_type="widget"
																data-widget_type="pxl_services_list.default">
																<div class="elementor-widget-container">
																	<div class="pxl-services-list layout-3">
																		<div class="row">
																			<div class="col-6 content">
																				<div id="item-bc4d640"
																					class="box-content active">
																					<div class="item-image">
																						<div class="col-auto">
																							<img loading="lazy"
																								decoding="async"
																								class="no-lazyload "
																								src="./assets/img21-home2-1-424x565.webp"
																								width="424" height="565"
																								alt="img21-home2"
																								title="img21-home2">
																						</div>
																					</div>
																					<div class="sub-des">
																						<div class="item-subtitle">
																							Dec
																							2, 2025
																						</div>
																						<div class="item-description">
																							As fuel demand grows across
																							Southern Africa, transport
																							safety has become a top
																							priority. This article
																							explores how modern fuel
																							haulage companies are
																							improving tanker standards,
																							driver training, and route
																							risk management to ensure
																							safer and compliant fuel
																							deliveries.</div>
																					</div>
																				</div>
																				<div id="item-e044adb"
																					class="box-content ">
																					<div class="item-image">
																						<div class="col-auto">
																							<img loading="lazy"
																								decoding="async"
																								class="no-lazyload "
																								src="./assets/img9-home2-424x565.webp"
																								width="424" height="565"
																								alt="img9-home2"
																								title="img9-home2">
																						</div>
																					</div>
																					<div class="sub-des">
																						<div class="item-subtitle">
																							Dec
																							31, 2025
																						</div>
																						<div class="item-description">
																							Road transport remains the
																							backbone of regional
																							logistics. We break down how
																							efficient fleet management,
																							real-time tracking, and
																							cross-border coordination
																							are helping businesses move
																							goods faster and more
																							reliably across Zimbabwe and
																							neighboring markets..</div>
																					</div>
																				</div>
																				<div id="item-8cff320"
																					class="box-content ">
																					<div class="item-image">
																						<div class="col-auto">
																							<img loading="lazy"
																								decoding="async"
																								class="no-lazyload "
																								src="./assets/img7-home2-424x565.webp"
																								width="424" height="565"
																								alt="img7-home2"
																								title="img7-home2">
																						</div>
																					</div>
																					<div class="sub-des">
																						<div class="item-subtitle">
																							Jan
																							30, 2026
																						</div>
																						<div class="item-description">
																							From GPS fleet tracking to
																							digital dispatch systems,
																							technology is reshaping
																							transport operations. This
																							article highlights the key
																							logistics technologies
																							improving delivery accuracy,
																							reducing downtime, and
																							enhancing customer
